  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/a05831f3a9213fc7f26b3832a4aff9e4.poster.avif?t=1586454197\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/a05831f3a9213fc7f26b3832a4aff9e4.webm?t=1586454197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/a05831f3a9213fc7f26b3832a4aff9e4.mp4?t=1586454197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>I bet you don't have enough patience, enough strength, enough smartness to complete this journey...<br><strong>Bastard Little Zombie</strong> is an impossible Platformer/Puzzle/Trial-And-Error game, one of the hardest and most challenging indie platformer you'll play.<br>It's going to be very tough to keep going and the road to take won't always be so obvious... <strong>Will you make it?</strong><br><br>•Explore and beat 3 nearly impossible levels.<br><br>•Each level has its own handcrafted environment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/7fcad4bde4ba8e35662b43ea048dadb7.avif?t=1586454197\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>•Figure out the next move to make in order to beat the level.<br><br>•Find the right road to take to move forward.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/b0cae1e82f1843e177d06319007ace96.avif?t=1586454197\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><i>This game was created by a single developer and this is his first project.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/a05831f3a9213fc7f26b3832a4aff9e4.poster.avif?t=1586454197\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/a05831f3a9213fc7f26b3832a4aff9e4.webm?t=1586454197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/a05831f3a9213fc7f26b3832a4aff9e4.mp4?t=1586454197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>I bet you don't have enough patience, enough strength, enough smartness to complete this journey...<br><strong>Bastard Little Zombie</strong> is an impossible Platformer/Puzzle/Trial-And-Error game, one of the hardest and most challenging indie platformer you'll play.<br>It's going to be very tough to keep going and the road to take won't always be so obvious... <strong>Will you make it?</strong><br><br>•Explore and beat 3 nearly impossible levels.<br><br>•Each level has its own handcrafted environment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/7fcad4bde4ba8e35662b43ea048dadb7.avif?t=1586454197\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>•Figure out the next move to make in order to beat the level.<br><br>•Find the right road to take to move forward.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1273890/extras/b0cae1e82f1843e177d06319007ace96.avif?t=1586454197\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><i>This game was created by a single developer and this is his first project.</i>",
